What can you expect at TreasureFest in 2024?

✨Local: Imagine everything you love about the Bay Area all in one place. Experience local music, art, food, creators, and community at TreasureFest! 

✨Music: You can expect a groovy lineup of our talented local music scene!

✨Food: Satisfy your taste buds with an array of local flavors, from street food to gourmet delicacies!

✨Art:  Get ready for eyebrow-raising installations, collaborative pieces, and lots of local artwork!

✨Creators: Discover hundreds of local emerging brands, vintage curators, designers, makers, artists, HomeGoods, and crafts!

✨Connect: TreasureFest is not just an event; it’s a chance to connect with like-minded individuals who share your passion for community, art, and culture!

Join us at TreasureFest on Treasure Island Feb 24th-25th from 10am-4pm where local talents, music, food, art, creators, and connections come together to create an unforgettable experience. Don’t miss out!

Announcing Danielle Cohen as our new Event Director for TreasureFest!

Danielle has 15+ years of experience managing community events that support local artists & businesses!

In 2005, while working out of a SoMa art gallery, Danielle launched an event production company called Missing Piece, where she produced over 50, award winning,  art gallery and runway shows in the Bay Area. 
 
In 2012, Danielle founded Urban Air Market, a curated marketplace for sustainable design and expanded the market from its original location in Hayes Valley, San Francisco to Oakland, Los Angeles, Portland, Seattle, and Atlanta. Each market attracted 5,000+ attendees and showcased over 100 designers of fashion, accessories, body products, home decor, furniture and art.

Danielle’s reputation as a champion for small businesses and artists along with her extensive experience in event planning and management will be a major boost to our loyal and growing TreasureFest community. We are excited to have her leadership and support for our much-anticipated re-launch of TreasureFest. 
 
Please join us in wishing her a warm welcome!

Calling all creators, artists, and brands, join us at TreasureFest! Seize this opportunity to showcase your talent in front of thousands of local attendees and to be part of an event that celebrates your craft, your brand, and your uniqueness.
